    </edge>
    <data key="d0">Oportun: Increasing the Accuracy of SensitiveData Discovery Using Amazon Macie</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-kA0ahrhX3I</data>
    <data key="d2">Oportun's architecture to solve the business challenge of identifying and protecting sensitive member data (e.g., SSNs, ITINs, government IDs) across multiple AWS accounts, starting with production. The core solution leverages Amazon Macie to scan S3 buckets and generate findings metadata, which is then analyzed using Amazon Athena, processed by AWS Glue, and visualized in Amazon QuickSight dashboards. This enables Security Engineers to identify risky buckets and remediate data security posture. A self-built MySQL data lake also stores processed findings. The system achieves 95% accuracy for critical sensitive data types.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, control, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
